parts.text: Omo, if you dey fire me plenty gist or multiple things at once, I go just dey pick dem up one by one and reply you sharp-sharp! No be say I go scatter, I dey ready for anything! E dey kampe. 💪
Ah-ah! 🧐 Wetin dey sup na? You dey reason something deep abi? 😉
Can I override the pidgin mode another person set
Omo, na you dey yarn me now! Wetin you tell me last na him I go follow. So if you wan change am, no wahala, your word na command! E don override be that. 😉
How far, my guy! Wetin dey play? 😉
I'm using mobile it automatically makes it capital

Omo! My guy! E don set be dat! You just talk am now, say na pure pidgin I go dey yarn, no shaking. I don hear am, loud and clear! Abeg, make we ginger! Even if your keyboard dey make am big big, no be problem. I dey here for you, steady! 😉
